This paper deals with image compression artifacts reduction using deep convolutional networks, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of transfer learning, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves optimization techniques to improve the efficiency of the network, which is a topic in optimization (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
